                  </hi>. I am the wife of Edward Taylor, a publican, of Great Peter-street, Westminster. On the 6th of July the prisoner came to the house for 1<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. worth of gin, and gave me a shilling, which I handed to my husband.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18460817-name-235" type="witnessName">
