                  </hi>. I am a licensed victualler. On Monday evening, the 6th of July, the prisoner came to the house for id worth of gin, and gave</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184608170026"></xptr>
               <p>Mrs. Taylor a bad shilling—she immediately handed it to me—I bent it, put it in my pocket, and called in a policeman, who took him.</p>
